===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|رَجَبٌ}}''' {{IPAchar|(rájab)}} {{m}}

#[[Rajab]], the seventh of the twelve months of the Muslim lunar calendar, each beginning with a [[new moon]]. [[Rajab]] means "respect" or "honor" in Arabic, and fighting is forbidden.

